OL,3,CDermatology patients face six-month
OL,4,Cwait for first appointment
OL,6,FDermatology waiting lists have soared
OL,7,Fin with hundreds of patients waiting
OL,8,Fmonths or even up to a year to be seen.
OL,10,FFigures show that more than 750
OL,11,Fpatients are waiting more than six
OL,12,Fmonths for their first dermatology
OL,13,Fappointment.
OL,15,FPatient Jean Lelliott was first
OL,16,Freferred by her GP nine months ago and
OL,17,Fsays at Christmas she was told she was
OL,18,Fon a waiting list for an appointment.
