OL,6,FHowever, when she phoned up to check
OL,7,Flast week she says the hospital
OL,8,Fexplained they did not have her
OL,9,Fdoctor's letter and she was not on any
OL,10,Fwaiting list.
OL,12,FJean added: "It means I go back to the
OL,13,Fqueue again I guess.
OL,15,F"I would say to anyone who hasn't had
OL,16,Fa letter to say they're on a waiting
OL,17,Flist to check that they haven't been
OL,18,Flost in the system somewhere."
OL,20,FJean has since been offered an
OL,21,Fappointment in June.
