OL,6,FDermatologist Dr Ian Whitcroft says he
OL,7,Fhas seen new patient referrals
OL,8,Fquadruple since the Covid pandemic.
OL,10,FHe explained: "I think it's a problem
OL,11,Feverywhere. I talk to my hospital
OL,12,Fcolleagues, we're all struggling
OL,13,Fbecause the post-pandemic tidal wave
OL,14,Fhad a great impact and you're trying
OL,15,Fto play catch up on top of an already
OL,16,Fbusy workload, it's very difficult."
OL,18,FIn a statement, the government said
OL,19,Fthey are trying to deploy additional
OL,20,Fresources to work through the backlog.
